## 7. To check the number is prime or not
```

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
int i,n,remainder = 1;
printf("enter a number");
scanf("%d",&n);
for(i = 2; i <= n/2; i++)
{
if(n % i == 0)                                             {
remainder = 0;
break;
}
}
if(remainder == 1)
{
printf("%d number is prime",n);
}
else
{
printf("%d is not a prime number",n);
}
```
**Output**
```
enter a number11
11 number is prime
```
